title: Jordan Love vs. Justin Herbert & DJ's Updated Top 50 Prospects
itunes:title: Jordan Love vs. Justin Herbert & DJ's Updated Top 50 Prospects
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys breakdown and compare Oregon QB Justin Herbert and Utah State QB Jordan Love (4:35). Then, the pair discuss the scenario of the Dolphins possibly passing on Alabama QB Tua Tagovailoa (16:08). Next, they explain if Oklahoma QB Jalen Hurts will prove everyone wrong (21:47). After that, the guys compliment the Alabama wide receivers by emphasizing how talented they are (27:01). To wrap up the show, DJ gives a few names that are in his updated top 50 prospects list (31:25).
